<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi><note n="333-1">The <hi rend="italic">puḷḷi</hi> is clearly marked in this inscription; the date is omitted.</note>matiraikoṇṭa kopparakecaripaṉmaṟku yāṇṭu teṉkarai tevatā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉap piramateyam Aṟiñcikaiccatu<hi rend="grantha">rvvedi</hi> maṅkalamāṉa I
<lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">grā</hi> mattukku <hi rend="grantha">sarvvaśā</hi> n
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tikaramāy <hi rend="grantha">sarvvābhyuda</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha"> samṛddhyarttha</hi> māka Iruntaruḷiirunta Araṇaḻi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ppa mākāḷattuk kāḷā<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi> ṭāriyāṉa cāttaṉūrnaṅkaikku vaṭakarai <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>teṭakki Ulakan vaitta nel Aimpatin kalam kalattuvāyt tiṅkaḷ Irunāḻi palicai
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yāl Āṭṭu pannirukala varai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
